A pancake store which sells traditional and modern pancakes. Love their fragrant peanut sauce instead of old style peanut which tends to fall out when biting. Each bite is full of crunchy peanut sauce filling.

I Started with their modern filling pancake though and they had various flavours cheese and encased in 2 round pancake.

Love each and every of them so far. But it can be a long wait if they run out of the skin. So order in advance before buying other stuff.
Tried the Original Hazelnut, O. peanut, O. biscoff and also the charcoal version. Love the crispy sides of the pancake and the generous fillings! Good for mid day snack too! Staff is generous as well

staff were very friendly, tried the biscoff pancake and it was pretty good and unique considering i‚Äôve never tried one with biscoff and the filling were pretty packed as you can see the filling were spilling out of both sides!!

recommend it, they offered to heat it up for me as well!
